Gameplay 26-1 - Old Friends

The girl’s consciousness slowly floated up from the abyssal darkness.

Her most vivid memories played before her eyes.

???: Who… is he?

???: …Did I kill him?

The girl was grief-stricken.

Although the memories were fragmented, the pangs of guilt had tormented her for a long time.

The victim must have been…

No. No matter who the handsome man lying in the pool of blood was… the girl had let him down.

A drop of water fell on the girl’s cheek, awakening her consciousness.

The man turned his vacant gaze to something behind the girl.

The girl wanted to turn around to see what he was looking at…

But her body wouldn’t respond to her commands.

[Ah… So he was…]

[…]

[But… Why does it seem like he’s crying?]

[Was it because of… that promise?]

[I can’t witness that moment… I didn’t know it would matter so much to you…]

[But I can tell… that you aren’t looking at me.]

[What is it that you are so upset about…]

Another drop of water fell upon the girl’s cheek.

She lost consciousness once again.

???: …Relax. You were just having a nightmare.

A calm voice seemed to come from far away. The girl tried to open her eyes, but all she saw was darkness.

???: Ah. You haven’t recovered your eyesight yet… But don’t worry, that’s normal when waking up from such a deep hibernation.

The mysterious voice gradually filtered into her dream.

???: In about an hour, your body will regain its functions.

???: Before that, I want to give you some basic information about the Current Era.

???: Right… Do you know who I am? If you do, try to nod your head.

The girl tried to remember how to move her muscles. After a few seconds, she managed to nod her head several times.

She felt like stretching, but her arms still wouldn’t obey her commands to move.

???: Excellent. There’s no need to rush, your limbs will regain mobility with time.

???: Anyway, I have some information to share with you.

???: Currently it is May of 2017 AD… Uh, sorry. Putting it that way might just confuse you further.

???: In other words - It is now 520 years after you entered hibernation.

